Brief Summary
=============

LogCHEM system is a tool for discriminative interactive mining of
chemical fragments. 


Installation
============

Please run the install.sh <install dir> script available in LogCHEM's
root directory . It will verify all dependencies required by LogCHEM and
install LogCHEM in the given directory. See INSTALL for more details.

Dependencies
============

LogCHEM runs on Linux and Unix Operating Systems.  The install.sh
script in LogCHEM's root directory makes use of Bash. All other
dependencies are verified by the install.sh script.

